      "description": "This 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman is a true showroom-quality specimen, meticulously maintained by a single enthusiast owner. The exterior shines in a deep Jet Black Metallic finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures a mirror-like reflection with zero rock chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the Black leather sport seats show no bolster wear, and the tactile surfaces still retain their factory-fresh matte finish. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete documented service history from authorized Porsche centers and having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Every button, switch, and mechanical component operates exactly as it did the day it left Stuttgart. This is an uncompromising choice for the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
